---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms & Conditions" description="The terms for booking and working with Studio Moire in Casablanca.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="container-reading flex flex-col gap-4 text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl mb-2">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-mute">Last updated 2025. Studio Moire, Casablanca.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Bookings</h2>
      <p>Sending a request does not confirm a booking. We reply with the next available option; your shoot is confirmed once you accept it. No payment is taken until you confirm the selected option.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Changes &amp; cancellations</h2>
      <p>You can adjust a request after submitting — the confirmation email includes an edit link and a direct reply address for small changes. Please give as much notice as you can for date changes.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Your content</h2>
      <p>Garments, references, and materials you bring remain yours. We agree image usage for each shoot in writing before delivery.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Write to <a class="underline decoration-accent underline-offset-4" href="mailto:hello@studio-moire.example">hello@studio-moire.example</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
